FBIS3-54666 "drsov001_u_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 Latvia Former Prime Minister Godmanis Quits Politics LD0201203194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1642 GMT 2 Jan 94 LD0201203194 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Kuchina] [Text] Riga January 2 TASS -- After studies in Germany ex-Latvian Premier Ivars Godmanis realized Latvians have little economic knowledge. It was the first detailed TV interview of Godmanis after the resignation of his government. The ex-premier said he will no longer involve in politics after the Popular Front's defeat at the summer parliament elections. Godmanis admitted the reform methods were merciless.
